{"id":391135,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/05/多吉犬兵卫：牛皮吹破之后碍国人士的打滚儿与泄/","date":"2015-05-02T03:31:13Z","modified":"2015-09-27T10:35:17Z","title":"多吉犬兵卫：牛皮吹破之后碍国人士的打滚儿与泄愤","content":"<p>来源：新浪微博</p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/3163212323/CfS5uj0zZ\">@多吉犬兵卫</a>：#无证据，不轻信#尼泊尔地震后，碍国人士诸如鲍迪克 之类相继编造了中国飞机占机场，尽显“大锅砂纹主义”等谣言。被戳破后他们不仅不检讨道歉，反而继续打滚儿造出更多谣言，并向受灾同胞泄愤。这次就对他们的后续谣言逐一辟谣，展示下他们欺软怕硬的恶习。（附前作）#尼泊尔地震#</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/尼泊尔a1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-391136\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/尼泊尔a1.jpg\" alt=\"尼泊尔a1\" width=\"425\" height=\"\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/尼泊尔a2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-391137\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/尼泊尔a2.jpg\" alt=\"尼泊尔a2\" width=\"425\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/尼泊尔a2.jpg 439w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/尼泊尔a2-25x300.jpg 25w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 439px) 100vw, 439px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/尼泊尔a3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-391138\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/尼泊尔a3.jpg\" alt=\"尼泊尔a3\" width=\"425\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/尼泊尔a3.jpg 439w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/尼泊尔a3-91x1024.jpg 91w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 439px) 100vw, 439px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/尼泊尔b1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-391139\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/尼泊尔b1.jpg\" alt=\"尼泊尔b1\" width=\"425\" height=\"\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/尼泊尔b2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-391140\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/fil